1. Metrics:

Metrics is the process of evaluating how well our model performed against train and test data

Regression:
    When the target is continuous data. whatever year u give, output will vary continuously

    ex: Gold price, Age, House Price.

    metrics - r2_score, mean_absolute_error, mean_squared_error #interview question

    #Based on data, you have to choose regression or classification.

Classification:
    When the target is categorical data or non continuous data. Means output will be discrete.

    ex: degree, qualification, cancer, spam mail

    metrics - accuracy_score, classification_report, confusion_matrix, f1_score, recall, precision #interview question

